The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Army exam to go online 
                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                      Army exam to go online 
                            
	New Delhi, Oct. 28 (PTI): The armys promotion exams for young officers will go online before the end of this year.        
	The decision came at the bi-annual army commanders conference with the top brass approving the system.        
	About 10,000 young lieutenants, captains and majors take this written exam every year to test their calibre for promotion to the next rank.        
	The army commanders have approved the new examination pattern, which is currently being run on a trial basis, a senior officer in the army headquarters told PTI.        
	The new online exams can be taken by the officers at a centre near to their place of posting throughout the country anytime of the year.                                                                                                                                                           
